                                                                        to have the result after observing

    5. hoffnung ausdrÃ¼cken:  express hope
                    es wird schon nichts passieren.                          Nothing will happen
                            -----
                            ansonsten klare Aussage - otherwise clear statement
                            burda doldurucu olarak kullanÄ±lmÄ±ÅŸ.. 
                            schon kullanÄ±lmazsa bu cÃ¼mle sÃ¶z vermek ama sÃ¶zÃ¼n tutmazsa yalancÄ± oluyorsun.
